12 B. Under a plan of division, any domestic limited liability
13 company may, in the manner provided in this section, be divided into
14 two or more domestic limited liability companies. The division of a
15 domestic limited liability company in accordance with this section
16 and, if applicable, the resulting cessation of the existence of the
